[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7412] reduced LOC by replacing several instances of 
``Value::Int {}``
, 
``Value::Float{}``
, 
``Value::Bool {}``
, and 
``Value::String {}``
 with 
``Value::int()``
, 
``Value::float()``
, 
``Value::boolean()``
 and 
``Value::string()``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7318] Allow 
``$env``
 and mutable records to be mutated by 
``=``
 (closes #7110)
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7411] ensured that errore in 
``else``
 are forwarded appropriately
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7405] fix external completions; add a caret when there is overlap
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7398] Add quotes to hash file autocomplete
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7367] Make 
``seq``
 return a 
``ListStream``
 where possible
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7409] added arbitrary base 
``math log``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7408] Add 
``math tau``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7406] Fix 
``math e``
 usage text
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7396] fixed tab not working in vi editor mode
jntrnr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7388] removed and/or from 'help operators'
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7387] Fix input redirect for externals
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7385] Add OneOf shape to fix 
``else``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7383] Improve empty pipelines
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7241] Better errors when bash-like operators are used
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7375] removed use of deprecated 
``actions-rs/cargo``
 GH action
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7374] Fix 
``watch``
 for block+closure split
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7359] Pin CI jobs to Ubuntu 20.04
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7351] Make SQLite queries cancellable
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7348] Improve error message for illegal filenames on Windows
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7344] Overhaul 
``schema``
 command, remove database name
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7373] fixed semicolon doesn't work for some commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7355] fix 
``split list``
 when separater is the first element of list
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7370] removed redundant code mentioning ToCsv
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7360] bumped to dev build v0.72.2
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7357] add input_output_types() to 
``ansi gradient``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7312] add background colors to the ansi command
raccmonteiro added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7354] ``++=``
 appendAssign operator (#7346)
nibon7 fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7353] kill: don't show signal example on windows
JohnJohnstone 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7352] fixed menus in default config
Kangaxx-0 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7350] fixed 
``upsert``
 index of zero
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7349] Add comments for nu syntax shape
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7343] fixed an issue with showing the wrong row index
dbuch landed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6806] Protocol: debug_assert!() Span to reflect a valid slice
